reviewText: This is a very "B" vintage film.  I'm not sure why, but I enjoyed it and have watched it a few times.
This was a low budget movie which although wasn't great, was enjoyable.
for it's quality and story line good old b&w movie for the age well worth  the money would buy this sort of film again
It's wonderful to be able to find older films as I work to complete an ancestry library project for a special gift.  Good condition and quick delivery!
